'''Projectile detonators''' were small explosives that were launched from either a wrist-mounted launcher or a [[Slugthrower/Legends|slugthrower]], that exploded on impact. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] carried one on a [[Bandolier/Legends|bandolier]] while wearing [[Ubese raider armor]]

